text: "So Real" is a 2000 song by Mandy Moore. It is from a album reissue I Wanna Be with You. It went to number 21 in Australia and number 18 in New Zealand. ==Track listings== Australian CD single # "So Real" # "Candy" (Wade Robson Remix) # "Not Too Young" # "So Real" (Wade Robson Remix) # "So Real" (video clip) French promo CD—"C'est si facile" #"C'est si facile" – 3:50 #"So Real" – 3:51 ==References== Category:2000 songs Category:Mandy Moore songs Category:Teen pop songs
